{% block form %}

  <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">You cannot claim Attendance Allowance if you get DLA</h1>

  <p class="govuk-body">If you are already getting Disability Living Allowance, 
  you are not eligible for Attendance Allowance.</p>

  <p class="govuk-body">If you submit an application for Attendance Allowance, your existing 
  benefits will be reviewed which may result in a change to what you currently get.</p>

  <p class="govuk-body"><a class="govuk-link" target=”_blank” href="https://www.gov.uk/dla-disability-living-allowance-benefit">Find out more about DLA</a>, including how to 
  <a class="govuk-link" target=”_blank” href="https://www.gov.uk/dla-disability-living-allowance-benefit/your-DLA-claim">report a change to your care needs or circumstances</a>.</p>

